@doclean v0.2
# Machine-readable API spec. Each @endpoint block is one API call.
@api The Plaid API
@base https://production.plaid.com
@version 2020-09-14_1.334.0
@auth ApiKey PLAID-CLIENT-ID in header | ApiKey Plaid-Version in header | ApiKey PLAID-SECRET in header
@endpoints 198
@toc Retrieve real-time balance data, Retrieve accounts, Retrieve information about a Plaid application, Create Asset Report Audit Copy, Retrieve an Asset Report Audit Copy, Remove Asset Report Audit Copy, Create an Asset Report, Filter Asset Report, Retrieve an Asset Report, Retrieve a PDF Asset Report, Refresh an Asset Report, Delete an Asset Report, Retrieve auth data, Get balance of your Bank Transfer account, Cancel a bank transfer, Create a bank transfer, List bank transfer events, Sync bank transfer events, Retrieve a bank transfer, List bank transfers, Migrate account into Bank Transfers, Retrieve a sweep, List sweeps, Retrieve information from the bank accounts used for employment verification, Create transaction category rule, Return a list of rules created for the Item associated with the access token., Remove transaction rule, enhance locally-held transaction data, Get Categories, Retrieve an Asset Report with Freddie Mac format. Only Freddie Mac can use this endpoint., Create Asset or Income Report Audit Copy Token, Remove an Audit Copy token, Update an Audit Copy Token, Retrieve information from the bank accounts used for income verification, Retrieve information from the bank accounts used for income verification in PDF format, Refresh a user's bank income information, Retrieve a summary of an individual's employment information, Retrieve an Asset Report with Freddie Mac format (aka VOA - Verification Of Assets), and a Verification Of Employment (VOE) report if this one is available. Only Freddie Mac can use this endpoint., Retrieve a user's payroll information, Check income verification eligibility and optimize conversion, Refresh a digital payroll income verification, Create a relay token to share an Asset Report with a partner client (beta), Retrieve the reports associated with a relay token that was shared with you (beta), Refresh a report of a relay token (beta), Remove relay token (beta), Retrieve Link sessions for your user, Retrieve a dashboard user, List dashboard users, Create a deposit switch without using Plaid Exchange, Create a deposit switch, Retrieve a deposit switch, Create a deposit switch token, Search employer database, (Deprecated) Retrieve a summary of an individual's employment information, Webhook receiver for fdx notifications, Retrieve identity data, Retrieve identity match score, Create a new identity verification, Retrieve Identity Verification, List Identity Verifications, Retry an Identity Verification, (Deprecated) Create an income verification instance, (Deprecated) Download the original documents used for income verification, (Deprecated) Retrieve information from the paystubs used for income verification, (Deprecated) Check digital income verification eligibility and optimize conversion, (Deprecated) Retrieve information from the tax documents used for income verification, Get details of all supported institutions, Get details of an institution, Search institutions, Get Investment holdings, Get investment transactions, Invalidate access_token, List a historical log of user consent events, List a user’s connected applications, Update the scopes of access for a particular application, Retrieve an Item, Import Item, Create public token, Exchange public token for an access token, Remove an Item, Update Webhook URL, Retrieve Liabilities data, Exchange the Link Correlation Id for a Link Token, Create Link Token, Get Link Token, Create Link Delivery session, Get Link Delivery session, Creates a new end customer for a Plaid reseller., Enables a Plaid reseller's end customer in the Production environment., Returns a Plaid reseller's end customer., Returns OAuth-institution registration information for a given end customer., Removes a Plaid reseller's end customer., Create payment consent, Get payment consent, Execute a single payment using consent, Revoke payment consent, Create a payment, Get payment details, List payments, Reverse an existing payment, Create payment token, Create payment recipient, Get payment recipient, List payment recipients, Create payment profile, Get payment profile, Remove payment profile, Create Apex bank account token, Retrieve Auth data, Retrieve Balance data, Create a bank transfer as a processor, Retrieve Identity data, Report whether you initiated an ACH transaction, Evaluate a planned ACH transaction, Report a return for an ACH transaction, Create Stripe bank account token, Create processor token, Manually fire a Bank Transfer webhook, Simulate a bank transfer event in Sandbox, Manually fire an Income webhook, Fire a test webhook, Force a Sandbox Item into an error state, Set verification status for Sandbox account, Save the selected accounts when connecting to the Platypus Oauth institution, Reset the login of a Payment Profile, Create a test Item and processor token, Create a test Item, Manually fire a Transfer webhook, Trigger the creation of a repayment, Simulate a transfer event in Sandbox, Simulate creating a sweep, Advance a test clock, Create a test clock, Get a test clock, List test clocks, Report whether you initiated an ACH transaction, Evaluate a planned ACH transaction, Opt-in an Item to Signal, Report a return for an ACH transaction, Enrich locally-held transaction data, Get transaction data, Fetch recurring transaction streams, Refresh transaction data, Get incremental transaction updates on an Item, Create a transfer authorization, Cancel a transfer, Get RTP eligibility information of a transfer, Create a transfer, List transfer events, Sync transfer events, Retrieve a transfer, Create a transfer intent object to invoke the Transfer UI, Retrieve more information about a transfer intent, List transfers, Migrate account into Transfers, Create a new originator, Get status of an originator's onboarding, Get status of all originators' onboarding, Generate a Plaid-hosted onboarding UI URL., Cancel a recurring transfer., Create a recurring transfer, Retrieve a recurring transfer, List recurring transfers, C